### Wrap RxStorage with encryption-crypto-js

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/encryption.html

This snippet demonstrates how to wrap a standard RxStorage (like `getRxStorageLocalstorage`) with the `wrappedKeyEncryptionCryptoJsStorage` plugin to enable encryption. This is a prerequisite for creating an encrypted RxDatabase.

```javascript
import { wrappedKeyEncryptionCryptoJsStorage} from 'rxdb/plugins/encryption-crypto-js';
import { getRxStorageLocalstorage } from 'rxdb/plugins/storage-localstorage';

// wrap the normal storage with the encryption plugin
const encryptedStorage = wrappedKeyEncryptionCryptoJsStorage({
    storage: getRxStorageLocalstorage()
});
```

