### Wrap RxStorage with crypto-js Encryption

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs-src/docs/encryption.md

This snippet demonstrates how to wrap a standard RxStorage, such as `getRxStorageLocalstorage`, with the `wrappedKeyEncryptionCryptoJsStorage` plugin to enable password-based encryption. This process is essential for securing data stored by RxDB.

```typescript
import {
    wrappedKeyEncryptionCryptoJsStorage
} from 'rxdb/plugins/encryption-crypto-js';
import { getRxStorageLocalstorage } from 'rxdb/plugins/storage-localstorage';

// wrap the normal storage with the encryption plugin
const encryptedStorage = wrappedKeyEncryptionCryptoJsStorage({
    storage: getRxStorageLocalstorage()
});
```

