### Renamed Encryption Plugin in RxDB

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs-src/docs/releases/14.0.0.md

The RxDB encryption plugin has been renamed from 'encryption' to 'encryption-crypto-js' to allow for alternative encryption implementations in the future. The import statement for the wrapped key encryption storage has been updated accordingly.

```typescript
// Instead of 
// import { wrappedKeyEncryptionStorage } from 'rxdb/plugins/encryption';
// it is now
import { wrappedKeyEncryptionCryptoJsStorage } from 'rxdb/plugins/encryption-crypto-js';
```

