### Define RxDB Encrypted Fields in Schema

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/releases/9.0.0.html

Demonstrates how to define encrypted fields at the top level of the RxDB schema. This simplifies schema management compared to older methods. The 'encrypted' array lists the fields to be encrypted.

```javascript
{
    "title": "my schema",
    "version": 0,
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {},
    "encrypted": [
        "password"
    ]
}
```

